类 CheckEol

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class CheckEol
extends org.apache.tools.ant.Task
    Ant task that checks that all the files in the given fileset have end-of-line delimiters that are appropriate for the current OS.

    The goal is to check whether we have problems with svn:eol-style property when files are committed on one OS and then checked on another one.
